  "text": "In biomimetic membranes as well as in cells, remarkable phenomena occur in the regime of larger deformations: cristaelike invaginations [CITATION_1] , tubulation [CITATION_2] , pearling [CITATION_3] , budding, exo-or endocytosis [CITATION_4] , etc. To study such phenomena, it would be useful to pursue our study in the nonlinear regime.",
